title: Cruz: 'Plausible' Coronavirus Came from a Lab in China
description: In a Wednesday interview with Fox Business Network's "Mornings with Maria," Sen. Ted Cruz (R-TX) suggested it is "plausible" to believe the coronavirus came from a lab in China. | Clips
content:
